# UIKeyboardHIDUsage.keyboardErrorUndefined

**Case**

The raw usage code 3 (decimal)/03 (hexadecimal).

## Declaration

```swift
case keyboardErrorUndefined
```

## Error keys

- **UIKeyboardHIDUsage.keyboardErrorRollOver**: The raw usage code 1 (decimal)/01 (hexadecimal).
